%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=195075203368286766437cd6_46807144"/><published>2025-05-17T13:40:58+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>b38c9f3fd132ba3a345113cf3d2094ff</id><title>英國 移民白皮書 Technical Annex 第12段</title><updated>2025-05-17T13:44:47+08:00</updated><author><name>天網恢恢疏不漏</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-17T13:44:47+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572442649"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572442649"&gt;都寫到明想針對D乜嘢人啦&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="9" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/titter.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;11. However an illustrative assessment of the measure to raise the threshold to&lt;br/&gt;qualification for settlement has been produced. For those cohorts affected by the&lt;br/&gt;increase in the standard qualifying period for settlement to ten years visa demand is&lt;br/&gt;likely to fall, as some will be deterred from coming to the UK as a result of the longer&lt;br/&gt;time to settlement.&lt;span style="color: #ff0000; "&gt;Also, a number of those currently in the UK are likely to leave due&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #ff0000; "&gt;to it taking longer to gain settled status&lt;/span&gt;. In 2024 there were 121,602 grants of&lt;br/&gt;settlement excluding those whose initial category of leave was Asylum2&lt;br/&gt;. This numberis likely to increase in the next few years as more migrants become eligible for&lt;br/&gt;settlement due to the high level of inflows since 2021.&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31929961&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=195075203368286766437cd6_46807144"/><published>2025-05-17T13:44:47+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>02a0ba74e0deede8cbb18851e27ab860</id><title>。賤人鬥窮物。8蚊老水雞比飯。一蚊隻生豪</title><updated>2025-05-17T13:48:27+08:00</updated><author><name>edwin8888</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-17T13:48:27+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572442681"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572442681"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16231017" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572442681" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250517/20250517_a990e92812a3c6f18d170uUmiFUOizZs.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/00c9ea/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250517/20250517_a990e92812a3c6f18d170uUmiFUOizZs.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16231017_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16231017&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2024_1200_x_675_px_78_.png&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (304.9 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-5-17 13:48&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31929963&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=195075203368286766437cd6_46807144"/><published>2025-05-17T13:48:27+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>4a29bebf0cba6cc8d6531030c2601323</id><title>勁蝕跳船】北都私宅樓價7年蒸發逾330萬 跌價超過45% 原文網址：【勁蝕跳船】北都私宅樓價7年蒸發逾330萬 跌價超過45% | on.cc東網 | 產</title><updated>2025-05-17T14:14:17+08:00</updated><author><name>~kurapika~</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-17T14:14:17+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572442986"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572442986"&gt;蝕幅擴大，個別成交跌價幅度逾40%。利嘉閣何鑫表示，北區高爾夫·御苑7座高層C室，實用面積約375方呎，一房連開放式廚房間隔，外望高爾夫球場景，外區客睇樓後即洽購，終以400萬港元購入，呎價約10,667元。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：【勁蝕跳船】北都私宅樓價7年蒸發逾330萬跌價超過45% | on.cc東網 | 產經 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20250517%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20250517124014907-0517_00842_001.html%3FeventPath%3Dhk_finance%26eventID%3D4028810746381ccb014647a574963a2c&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=d9bf51880948a948a478b03f1ca2657a&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/fina ... ccb014647a574963a2c&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;299至啱價&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31929994&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=195075203368286766437cd6_46807144"/><published>2025-05-17T14:14:17+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>3e84973e76c105b83bd7556e95490072</id><title>美金轉弱 一手散貨. 息口.又夾 逃生門 5-6月</title><updated>2025-05-17T16:55:14+08:00</updated><author><name>seanball</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-17T16:55:14+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572444840"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572444840"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="51" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_40.gif"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="51" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_40.gif"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;老特貿戰開左逃生門俾發展商&lt;br/&gt;弱美金引到熱錢入港..假象&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;搞完IPO 錢一走..H按就會收緊..&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="55" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/smile_44.gif"/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;不過老美始終會有一日減息..我相信&lt;br/&gt;.供緊樓就堅持落去 希望在明天&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31930106&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=195075203368286766437cd6_46807144"/><published>2025-05-17T16:55:14+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>0f7a18330270a158a3c7e83caa7d27c5</id><title>亞特蘭大聯儲料今年減息一次 美國經濟不會陷入衰退</title><updated>2025-05-17T17:02:07+08:00</updated><author><name>好久冇見</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-17T17:02:07+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572444938"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572444938"&gt;亞特蘭大聯儲行長博斯蒂克（Raphael Bostic）預期，美國經濟今年將放緩，但不會陷入衰退，並重申他預計今年只會減息一次。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;博斯蒂克受訪時表示，一系列不確定性和擔憂給消費者帶來壓力，美國今年的經濟增長率可能在0.5%至1%的水平，貿易政策波動亦令企業在作出重要決策時更謹慎。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;他說，雖然對等關稅暫緩90天實施，同時美國和中國互降關稅，但很多談判的最終結果仍未明朗，重申估計今年聯儲局將會減息一次&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2069375/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E4%BA%9E%E7%89%B9%E8%98%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%96%99%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%B8%9B%E6%81%AF%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E4%B8%8D%E6%9C%83%E9%99%B7%E5%85%A5%E8%A1%B0%E9%80%80" target="_blank" uhash="99a81b308c4cd5706268e8f647ebeb3a"&gt;https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2069375/即時-財經-亞特蘭大聯儲料今年減息一次-美國經濟不會陷入衰退&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31930111&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=195075203368286766437cd6_46807144"/><published>2025-05-17T17:02:07+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>770b5b0a54307eb98e19b91af3b2f9b4</id><title>深港「極限通勤」三小時返工惹熱議 精打細算定自討苦吃？</title><updated>2025-05-17T17:14:09+08:00</updated><author><name>carters</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-17T17:14:09+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572445062"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572445062"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;深港「極限通勤」三小時返工惹熱議 精打細算定自討苦吃？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;有網民近日於討論區分享其「極限港深通勤」攻略，指自己每日由深圳北站往返香港，每日約需三小時。帖文隨即引起網民熱議，有人讚其「除笨有精」，認為深圳月租六、七千元，生活質素更高；亦有人直言舟車勞頓章苦，每日趕車令生活彈性盡失，掀起一場對通勤與生活取捨的激辯。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;p align="center"&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="572445062" original-img="https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/C43B1EuOBzUecQxotKxgyg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2NTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-05/cef386d0-30dc-11f0-9dcf-229dc1d1eeff" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/C43B1EuOBzUecQxotKxgyg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2NTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-05/cef386d0-30dc-11f0-9dcf-229dc1d1eeff" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/121ee9/f/800x0/https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/C43B1EuOBzUecQxotKxgyg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY2NTtjZj13ZWJw/https%3A//s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-05/cef386d0-30dc-11f0-9dcf-229dc1d1eeff"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #999; "&gt;深港「極限通勤」三小時返工惹熱議，精打細算定自討苦吃？資料圖片。 (Photo by Mao Siqian/Xinhua via Getty Images)·Xinhua News Agency via Getty Images&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;極限通勤&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;：7:42出門 8:45到公司&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;有網民在連登討論區詳細記錄「極限通勤」路線，稱自己每日早上7:42 出門，步行十分鐘到深圳北站搭高鐵，大約8:20抵達西九龍站，通關僅需15分鐘，0845 到達公司樓下，下班則「18:30 收工 19:40 番到屋企」，強調行程已盡量壓縮至最短時間。&lt;br/&gt;他解釋選擇在深圳居住，主要因為「居住環境寬敞舒適」、「生活成本與香港相若但質素提升」；但亦坦言此模式需嚴格配合高鐵班次時間，「高峰時段需要搶票，不能賴床」，生活節奏緊湊。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;p align="center"&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="572445062" original-img="https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/d2gF6A9tq0695ms2McvaIg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-05/a0443b90-30dc-11f0-bfb7-2719e275a723" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/d2gF6A9tq0695ms2McvaIg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-05/a0443b90-30dc-11f0-bfb7-2719e275a723" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/8ddbe7/f/800x0/https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/d2gF6A9tq0695ms2McvaIg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https%3A//s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-05/a0443b90-30dc-11f0-bfb7-2719e275a723"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #999; "&gt;據一名有網民在連登討論區通勤路線顯示，稱自己每日早上7:42 出門，約8:45分抵達公司樓下。資料圖片。 (Photo by Michael Ho Wai Lee/SOPA Images/LightRocket via Getty Images)·SOPA Images via Getty Images&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.5rem"&gt;車費加租金 貴過香港租樓？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;帖文引來大量留言，一方讚賞其「極限通勤」精打細算，另一方則冷嘲熱諷。支持者認為，深圳租樓選擇多、空間大、物價低，值得以時間成本換取生活質素：「1個鐘通勤時間已經好過80%香港人啦」、「高鐵仲要有位坐，唔似西鐵日日迫到癲咁」。&lt;br/&gt;反對者則指出隱藏成本高，假設月入1.8萬港元，每月20日上班的三小時交通成本價4000多元，而且長時間舟車勞頓累人，「比間皇宮你住都無用」。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.5rem"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;中立聲音：視乎地點與彈性&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;亦有網民持中立態度，認為是否值得，關鍵視乎公司地點及工時安排：「佢返西九龍，其實通勤時間唔算長。住沙田返鰂魚涌都要接近90分鐘」、「如果有一兩日WFH，其實幾合理」。不過有其他不可控風險，例如口岸封關、搬辦公室等情況，一旦變化，整個安排或「玩完」。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;p align="center"&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="572445062" original-img="https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xJqF5bSFrwqwEphITtHRbg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwOTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-05/32292bb0-30dd-11f0-bbdd-8b0395d3cd02" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xJqF5bSFrwqwEphITtHRbg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwOTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-05/32292bb0-30dd-11f0-bbdd-8b0395d3cd02" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/17e0af/f/800x0/https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xJqF5bSFrwqwEphITtHRbg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwOTtjZj13ZWJw/https%3A//s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-05/32292bb0-30dd-11f0-bbdd-8b0395d3cd02"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #999; "&gt;據中原地產網站顯示，全港低於12,000元租金放盤約有1,200個。（中原地產）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.5rem"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;深圳居住成本逾萬元&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;根據樓主說法，深圳住所月租約人民幣6,000元（約港幣6,500元），來回高鐵每月車費約港幣3,500元，合共約一萬元，兩者加起其實與香港租細單位相若。例如沙田金獅花園、粉嶺牽晴間等四、五百方呎單位，目前放租價約為1.2萬元，相近價位的納米樓或新界舊樓選擇更多，租金低至八、九千元，據中原地產網站顯示，全港低於12,000元租金放盤約有1,200個。&lt;br/&gt;對於住深圳返港上班，有人視之為提升生活質素的捷徑，有人則認為是為慳錢而犧牲生活本質。「極限通勤」是否可取，最終仍要看每個人自己的盤算。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%B7%B1%E6%B8%AF%E3%80%8C%E6%A5%B5%E9%99%90%E9%80%9A%E5%8B%A4%E3%80%8D%E4%B8%89%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E8%BF%94%E5%B7%A5%E6%83%B9%E7%86%B1%E8%AD%B0-%E7%B2%BE%E6%89%93%E7%B4%B0%E7%AE%97%E5%AE%9A%E8%87%AA%E8%A8%8E%E8%8B%A6%E5%90%83%EF%BC%9F-234851737.html" target="_blank" uhash="6f0d7dfaf946a46291191bedeb8b114e"&gt;https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/深港「極限通勤」三小時返工惹熱議-精打細算定自討苦吃？-234851737.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31930125&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=195075203368286766437cd6_46807144"/><published>2025-05-17T17:14:09+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>c20adeb5d59a88892871bc3e055824e9</id><title>【多相】兩房銀主居屋大幅劈價至僅110萬元推拍 呎價約2500元</title><updated>2025-05-17T17:30:05+08:00</updated><author><name>新25</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-17T17:30:05+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572445248"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572445248"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16231480" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572445248" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250517/20250517_4451fc0bc9b2fa698cb08IvWlucGd6n1.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/accd39/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250517/20250517_4451fc0bc9b2fa698cb08IvWlucGd6n1.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16231480_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16231480&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;image.png&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (342.78 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-5-17 17:30&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;新界未補價第二市場兩房居屋，銀主大幅減價至僅110萬元推拍，呎價約2,500元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="572445248" original-img="https://hk.on.cc/img/v2/truvid_fire.png" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://hk.on.cc/img/v2/truvid_fire.png" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/467212/f/800x0/https://hk.on.cc/img/v2/truvid_fire.png"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;其他熱爆話題：close&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;忠誠拍賣下周三(21日)將推拍的上述銀主盤，為上水翠麗花園3座低層L室，實用面積約427方呎，第二市場開價較之前調低70萬元，減幅約38.9%，呎價約2,576元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;該行指出，單位現時估價約160萬元，可承做九成半按揭。物業最新開價低約50萬元，差幅達約31.3%。&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：【多相】兩房銀主居屋大幅劈價至僅110萬元推拍呎價約2500元 | on.cc東網 | 產經&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20250517/bkn-20250517153439948-0517_00842_001.html" target="_blank" uhash="0eb11edda25b9eb6c705a17e391213df"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20250517/bkn-20250517153439948-0517_00842_001.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31930142&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=195075203368286766437cd6_46807144"/><published>2025-05-17T17:30:05+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>f42f91e86970e93f6f8ed9af98d1fad0</id><title>旭禾苑新居屋購5年即淪銀主盤 劈價35萬連裝修沽出</title><updated>2025-05-17T17:37:09+08:00</updated><author><name>新25</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-17T17:37:09+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572445316"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572445316"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16231486" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572445316" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250517/20250517_fff1efc7a33256d9c6e7ha9RGQAs8MK0.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/a449ac/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250517/20250517_fff1efc7a33256d9c6e7ha9RGQAs8MK0.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16231486_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16231486&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;image.png&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (229.15 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-5-17 17:37&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;市場再錄新居屋銀主盤成交個案。萬方地產葉搏麟表示，火炭旭禾苑高層10室，實用面積約393方呎，為兩房間隔，有裝修，銀主於未補價第二市場叫價415萬港元放售。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="572445316" original-img="https://hk.on.cc/img/v2/truvid_fire.png" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://hk.on.cc/img/v2/truvid_fire.png" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/467212/f/800x0/https://hk.on.cc/img/v2/truvid_fire.png"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;其他熱爆話題：close&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;他指，上址放盤約9個月，累減35萬元，減幅約8.4%，以380萬元售出，呎價約9,669元。資料顯示，單位於2020年5月一手購入價約271.2萬元，約5年帳面升值約40%。&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：旭禾苑新居屋購5年即淪銀主盤劈價35萬連裝修沽出 | on.cc東網 | 產經&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20250516/bkn-20250516214553221-0516_00842_001.html" target="_blank" uhash="4e3fc7fac681bcbc98fff605c273d561"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20250516/bkn-20250516214553221-0516_00842_001.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31930151&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=195075203368286766437cd6_46807144"/><published>2025-05-17T17:37:09+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>a36170da060ade5fa7f8c152c97c32fb</id><title>【勁蝕跳船】北都私宅樓價7年蒸發逾330萬 跌價超過45%</title><updated>2025-05-17T17:39:27+08:00</updated><author><name>新25</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-17T17:39:27+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572445344"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572445344"&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16231494" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572445344" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250517/20250517_5a12dc13b3bebf061e14FAvXbbk0CAil.png"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/801929/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250517/20250517_5a12dc13b3bebf061e14FAvXbbk0CAil.png"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16231494_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16231494&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;image.png&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (597.42 KB)&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-5-17 17:39&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;br/&gt;二手樓蝕幅擴大，個別成交跌價幅度逾40%。利嘉閣何鑫表示，北區高爾夫·御苑7座高層C室，實用面積約375方呎，一房連開放式廚房間隔，外望高爾夫球場景，外區客睇樓後即洽購，終以400萬港元購入，呎價約10,667元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="572445344" original-img="https://hk.on.cc/img/v2/truvid_fire.png" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://hk.on.cc/img/v2/truvid_fire.png" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/467212/f/800x0/https://hk.on.cc/img/v2/truvid_fire.png"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;其他熱爆話題：close&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;他指，原業主於2018年以約736.3萬元一手買入單位，持貨約7年帳蝕336.3萬元，單位貶值約45.6%。該屋苑現有約19個單位放售，入場費約393萬元。&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：【勁蝕跳船】北都私宅樓價7年蒸發逾330萬跌價超過45% | on.cc東網 | 產經&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20250517/bkn-20250517124014907-0517_00842_001.html" target="_blank" uhash="d20cd13e4224a684bc0fb242e0b1c917"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20250517/bkn-20250517124014907-0517_00842_001.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31930154&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=195075203368286766437cd6_46807144"/><published>2025-05-17T17:39:27+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>6a9311e84073eaa2d03368d26b9f6af8</id><title>埔嵐山三房戶780萬易手 原業主持貨11年帳面微蝕37.9萬</title><updated>2025-05-17T17:43:07+08:00</updated><author><name>你契爷係我</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-17T17:43:07+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572445390"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572445390"&gt;大埔 嵐山 新界 美聯物業大埔 -白石角豪宅分行助理區域經理黃國輝 (STEPHEN WONG)表示，近期市場觀望氣氛濃厚，部分買家趁機物色優質單位。該行最新促成大埔嵐山實用面積910方呎單位， 以780萬元獲新買家承接自用，2014年貨帳面輕微蝕讓約37.9萬元。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;黃國輝指出，成交單位為6座中層B室成交，實用面積910方呎，屬3房間隔。據悉，原業主以840萬元放盤後吸引區內換樓客洽詢，雙方經議價後以780萬元易手，實用呎價約8,571元。 資料顯示，原業主2014年以817.9萬元購入，帳面輕微蝕讓約37.9萬元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.edigest.hk/%E4%BA%8C%E6%89%8B%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4/%E5%B5%90%E5%B1%B1-%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94-%E6%96%B0%E7%95%8C-%E7%BE%8E%E8%81%AF%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD-%E4%BA%8C%E6%89%8B%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4-aplt-1830535/" target="_blank" uhash="b71b4403718fa0d9681ed08b06f7e396"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: 'Liberation Serif'"&gt;https://www.edigest.hk/二手成交/嵐山-大埔-新界-美聯物業-二手成交-aplt-1830535/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;[&lt;span style="font-style: italic;"&gt; 本帖最後由 你契爺係我 於 2025-5-17 17:50 編輯 &lt;/span&gt;]&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31930156&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=195075203368286766437cd6_46807144"/><published>2025-05-17T17:43:07+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>d410952b94eab3275ee09f8301c211f3</id><title>而家新樓都接近一萬蚊呎，點解仲有人去買第一城D舊樓？</title><updated>2025-05-17T17:44:10+08:00</updated><author><name>厲害了我的英國</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-05-17T17:44:10+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572445402"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572445402"&gt;又唔係地點好過人，又舊&lt;br&gt;重點係唔係平&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="embed-responsi